These Releases take a lot of Hardwork as Some Tracks Are Really Hard To Find. Please Note That These Are Full Length Mixes and are Ideal For DJiing. Support The DJ by following on the above links And I Will Continue Releasing These Every Month. I have put this release for free and i am getting no profit. 

Also, I host my own radio show - Trance Harmonics Radio every Thursday 4PM (CET) on www.tfb-radio.com.
